Create 4 social video template files for a Remotion project. All files go under `/Users/lhalicki/coding_projects/founder-workspace/development/_infrastructure/video-studio-template/src/templates/`.

IMPORTANT RULES:
- All animations MUST use `useCurrentFrame()` + `interpolate()` from "remotion" — NEVER CSS transitions
- Each template must export: the component (named export), a `calculateMetadata` function, and `defaultProps`
- Use `{ extrapolateRight: "clamp", extrapolateLeft: "clamp" }` on all interpolate calls
- Import shared components from `../components/` (TextOverlay, Logo, SlideTransition, NumberCounter, ProgressBar)
- Import hooks from `../hooks/` (useBrandKit, useAsset, useStockAsset)
- Import types from `../types` (BrandKit, TransitionType)
- Import timing utils from `../lib/timing` (secondsToFrames, totalFrames)
- Import `useCurrentFrame, useVideoConfig, interpolate, spring, Audio, Img, Sequence` from "remotion"
- Import `AbsoluteFill` from "remotion" for full-screen containers

## File 1: SocialReel.tsx
Animated text slides with transitions and background music. Default 9:16 (1080x1920) at 30fps.

```typescript
interface SocialReelProps {
  slides: Array<{ headline: string; body?: string; image?: string }>;
  brandKit?: Partial<BrandKit>;
  music?: string;
  durationPerSlide?: number; // seconds, default 3
  transition?: TransitionType; // default "slide"
  showLogo?: boolean; // default true
  ctaText?: string;
}
```

- Uses SlideTransition to sequence slides
- Each slide: full-screen branded background (brand background color) + TextOverlay headline (centered, large) + optional body text below + optional Img
- Final slide: Logo (center) + optional CTA text
- Background music via `<Audio>` if music prop provided, use useStockAsset for stock paths
- `calculateMetadata`: compute durationInFrames = (slides.length * durationPerSlide * fps) + (showLogo ? 2 * fps : 0)
- defaultProps: 5 sample slides with headlines

## File 2: SocialQuote.tsx
Quote card with animated text reveal. Default 1:1 (1080x1080) at 30fps.

```typescript
interface SocialQuoteProps {
  quote: string;
  author: string;
  authorTitle?: string;
  authorImage?: string;
  brandKit?: Partial<BrandKit>;
  music?: string;
  duration?: number; // seconds, default 8
}
```

- AbsoluteFill background with brand primary→secondary gradient (use inline style with linear-gradient)
- Large quote marks (decorative, e.g. `"` character at fontSize 200, opacity 0.15)
- Quote text reveals word-by-word using TextOverlay with animationType="word-by-word"
- Author attribution fades in (TextOverlay with enterFrame after quote would complete, estimate ~quote.split(" ").length * 3 + 15 frames)
- If authorImage: circular img (borderRadius: "50%", overflow: "hidden") that fades in with the author text
- Logo in bottom-right corner
- calculateMetadata: durationInFrames = duration * fps
- defaultProps: sample quote, author name, title

## File 3: SocialListicle.tsx
Numbered tips/points with slide transitions. Default 9:16 (1080x1920) at 30fps.

```typescript
interface SocialListicleProps {
  title: string;
  items: Array<{ number: number; text: string; icon?: string }>;
  brandKit?: Partial<BrandKit>;
  music?: string;
  durationPerItem?: number; // seconds, default 3
  transition?: TransitionType;
}
```

- Opening title slide (1.5s): title with TextOverlay slide-up animation on branded background
- Each item: large NumberCounter (animating from 0 to item.number) + TextOverlay (slide-up) for text
- Use SlideTransition between items
- Closing slide with Logo (center)
- calculateMetadata: durationInFrames = (1.5 + items.length * durationPerItem + 2) * fps
- defaultProps: "5 Tips" title with 5 numbered items

## File 4: SocialBeforeAfter.tsx
Split-screen comparison with wipe transition. Default 9:16 (1080x1920) at 30fps.

```typescript
interface SocialBeforeAfterProps {
  before: { label: string; image: string; description?: string };
  after: { label: string; image: string; description?: string };
  title?: string;
  brandKit?: Partial<BrandKit>;
  music?: string;
  duration?: number; // seconds, default 10
}
```

- Optional title slide at start (1.5s) if title provided
- "Before" full-screen with label overlay (3s): Img fills screen, TextOverlay label at bottom with semi-transparent backdrop
- Wipe transition (use interpolate to animate a clip-path or width from 0% to 100% over ~30 frames)
- "After" full-screen with label overlay (3s)
- Optional side-by-side view (2s): both images at 50% width
- calculateMetadata: durationInFrames based on sections (title 1.5s + before 3s + transition 1s + after 3s + comparison 2s)
- defaultProps: sample before/after with placeholder image paths and labels

After creating all 4 files, do NOT commit — just create the files.

