- Use SlideTransition between sections
- Closing slide (3s): Logo center + "Thank you" or brand tagline
- ProgressBar at bottom throughout
- calculateMetadata: durationInFrames = (3 + sections.length * durationPerSection + 3) * fps
- defaultProps: "How It Works" title with 3 sections

